title: One Life (Jabin Chavez)
description:
God wants your “yes.” In “One Life,” Pastor Jabin Chavez of City Life Church reminds us that when we submit our plans and problems to God, it creates space for Him to show up in our situation.

If you’ve just made a decision for Christ, please respond HERE: http://ele.vc/tIepfr
